text: Wilczyce may refer to the following places in Poland: *Wilczyce, Legnica County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Wilczyce, Wrocław County in Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Wilczyce, Lesser Poland Voivodeship (south Poland) *Wilczyce, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship (south-central Poland) *Wilczyce, Gmina Niegosławice in Lubusz Voivodeship (west Poland)
title: Wilczyce
